          <i class="fas fa-shield-halved text-green-600 text-xl"></i>
        </div>
        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Secure & Reliable</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Enterprise-grade security with Passport authentication, role-based access, and Google OAuth integration.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-purple-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-purple-200 transition-colors">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-bar text-purple-600 text-xl"></i>
