        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Advanced Analytics</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Detailed performance metrics, progress tracking, and comprehensive reporting for data-driven decisions.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="card group hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-200">
        <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-orange-100 rounded-lg flex items-center justify-center mb-4 group-hover:bg-orange-200 transition-colors">
          <i class="fas fa-mobile-alt text-orange-600 text-xl"></i>
