        <h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Mobile First</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-600">Fully responsive design that works perfectly on all devices - desktop, tablet, and mobile.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

